{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 74.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't tell just exactly how many he had killed or shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, I yanked him off the gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I yelled to another man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's-- whoever the sergeant there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, Sergeant, put somebody else on this gun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At the same time, when I ran over there, I drew my pistol-- my .45-- and fired it into the air several times to get everybody's attention.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was yelling, there'll be no more firing unless I give a specific order.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, the damage was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a small hospital unit right behind this wall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had-- I could see the red cross on the-- on the top of the building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we checked out the men that had been shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were about 11 that were dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some others were wounded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we took them into that hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was a German doctor there and a German medical crew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, then I ordered the company commander to move all of the prisoners out of the post as rapidly as possible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they rounded up then what was left of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was 11 dead and 7 or 8 that were wounded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the rest of them were all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we marched them off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then I got that thing halfway under-- what I thought was more or less under control.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard some firing then ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't see where it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I went then pretty rapidly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't waste any time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came out-- then, for the first time, I saw the prison area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Up to that time, it had been obscured by the buildings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I could not see it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
